</b></p>
<p><b>62. Continue its efforts and initiatives to spread education (Saudi Arabia); 
63. Strengthen policies to promote education and address educational 
</b></p>
<p><b>gender imbalances (Angola); 
64. Continue its efforts to ensure education for all children and to proceed, 
</b></p>
